        <Tag>TXT_KEY_BONUS_MANA_AIR_PEDIA</Tag>
        <English>Grants access to Air spells. This will allow Adepts to cast Windwall. Additional sources of this resource will increase the strength of Air Elementals summoned by Archmages.</English>
        <French>Grants access to Air spells. This will allow Adepts to cast Windwall. Additional sources of this resource will increase the strength of Air Elementals summoned by Archmages.</French>
